OL,3,CSacked minister breaks silence to
OL,4,Ccriticise Vaughan Gething's actions
OL,6,FThe Labour MS Hannah Blythyn has
OL,7,Fcriticised the way she was sacked from
OL,8,FVaughan Gething's government as a
OL,9,Fminister, claiming "proper process
OL,10,Fneeds to be put in place" and the
OL,11,Fsituation caused her "acute anxiety
OL,12,Fand stress".
OL,14,FShe claimed she was shown no evidence
OL,15,Ffor her removal and has raised "formal
OL,16,Fconcerns".
