OL,3,CSacked minister breaks silence to
OL,4,Ccriticise Vaughan Gething's actions
OL,6,FThe MS was sacked by First Minister
OL,7,FVaughan Gething in May this year over
OL,8,Fthe leaking of phone messages. At the
OL,9,Ftime Ms Blythyn denied leaking any
OL,10,Finformation, something she reasserted
OL,11,Fon Tuesday.
OL,13,FShe said: "I know I can look all my
OL,14,Fcolleagues that sit on these benches
OL,15,Fin the eye and say I have never leaked
OL,16,For briefed the media about any of you.
OL,17,FIn fact, I can say that to everyone in
OL,18,Fthe Siambr."
