OL,3,CSacked minister breaks silence to
OL,4,Ccriticise Vaughan Gething's actions
OL,6,FShe continued: "While I will not share
OL,7,Fthe detail, I will share that I have
OL,8,Fformally raised concerns about the
OL,9,Fprocess by which I was removed from
OL,10,Fgovernment; including not being shown
OL,11,Fany alleged evidence before being
OL,12,Fsacked, not being made aware that I
OL,13,Fwas under investigation and at no
OL,14,Fpoint was I advised, or was it
OL,15,Fevidenced, that I had broken the
OL,16,Fministerial code.
