OL,6,F"I absolutely recognise and respect it
OL,7,Fis within the gift of any first
OL,8,Fminister to appoint and remove members
OL,9,Fof their government. I understand the
OL,10,Fnature of politics and completely
OL,11,Faccept that.
OL,13,F"I raise concerns not out of self-
OL,14,Finterest but because I fundamentally
OL,15,Fbelieve in devolution and public
OL,16,Fservice. I have also very real
OL,17,Fconcerns that lessons have not been
OL,18,Flearned from the past.
