OL,6,F"Proper process needs to not only be
OL,7,Fput in place and followed for the
OL,8,Fdignity and respect of individuals
OL,9,Finvolved but also to uphold the
OL,10,Fintegrity of the civil service and the
OL,11,Foffice of the FM."
OL,13,FFollowing her leaving government, Ms
OL,14,FBlythyn was signed off work and was
OL,15,Fnot present to take part in the vote
OL,16,Fof no confidence in Vaughan Gething's
OL,17,Fleadership in June.
