OL,6,FSpeaking about her mental health at
OL,7,Fthe time, Ms Blythyn said: "I know
OL,8,Fthere has been speculation about my
OL,9,Fcircumstances and about whether I have
OL,10,Fbeen well enough to work.
OL,12,F"This has ranged from what is
OL,13,Ftantamount to misinformation and what
OL,14,Fcan be put down to misunderstanding.
OL,16,F"It should not be surprising that what
OL,17,Fhappened has been hugely detrimental
OL,18,Fto me on a personal level and led to
OL,19,Facute anxiety and stress.
