OL,3,CSacked minister breaks silence to
OL,4,Ccriticise Vaughan Gething's actions
OL,6,F"I have never been signed off work
OL,7,Fbefore...but there was a point when
OL,8,Fthe thought of just putting my camera
OL,9,Fon to vote and seeing you all
OL,10,Fliterally took my breath away.
OL,12,F"I share this now not in search of
OL,13,Fsympathy - I don't want people's
OL,14,Fsympathy - but because my recent
OL,15,Fexperience has brought home to me that
OL,16,Fwhile we all talk the talk on mental
OL,17,Fhealth, there is still more to do to
OL,18,Fimprove out understanding and the
OL,19,Fimpact it has on individuals and their
OL,20,Fability to do things we would
OL,21,Fordinarily take for granted."
