OL,6,FShe added: "Sadly I think we get so
OL,7,Fcaught up in the politics that we
OL,8,Fdon't think of the person.
OL,10,F"I am not broken but I know now more
OL,11,Fthan I did before that I am breakable,
OL,12,Fas we all are."
OL,14,FShe said it was a privilege to serve
OL,15,Fin the government, "particularly under
OL,16,Fthe leadership of Mark Drakeford".
