OL,6,FIn closing, she said: "In spite of the
OL,7,Fchallenges and difficulties - perhaps
OL,8,Fbecause of them - I feel a renewed
OL,9,Fsense of commitment to the politics of
OL,10,Fpublic service and a real
OL,11,Fdetermination to continue to
OL,12,Fcontribute to devolved democracy, my
OL,13,Fcommunity and our country."
OL,15,FResponding to the statement by Hannah
OL,16,FBlythyn in the Senedd, Andrew RT
OL,17,FDavies MS, Leader of the Welsh
OL,18,FConservatives, said: "Hannah Blythyn's
OL,19,Fcomments raise more questions for the
OL,20,FFirst Minister.
