OL,6,FThe First Minister's decision to sack
OL,7,FMs Blythyn followed a report on the
OL,8,FNation.Cymru news website which
OL,9,Ffeatured a message posted to a
OL,10,Fministerial group chat in August 2020
OL,11,Fby Mr Gething, stating that he was
OL,12,F"deleting the messages in this group".
OL,14,FHe said the leaked message was from a
OL,15,Fsection of an iMessage group chat with
OL,16,Fother Labour ministers and related to
OL,17,Finternal discussions within the Senedd
OL,18,FLabour group.
